Additionally, the paper discusses the practical importance of the problem in various domains, such as viral marketing, target advertisement, personalized recommendation, which suggests that it could also belong to the cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks) sub-category. The paper also mentions different solution methodologies proposed over the years, indicating that it could belong to the cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) sub-category.
